\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e+\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e Decent AoE\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e+\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e Ok DPS\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e−\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e Useful only in the early to mid game\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eB\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/toiletman-fruit-power-universal-piece.png?w=1200\" alt=\"Toilet Man Fruit Power from the Universal Piece Roblox experience.\"/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003eToilet Man\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e+\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e Decent DPS\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e−\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e Short range and AoE\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e−\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e Worst Epic Fruit Power\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eB\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/spin-fruit-power-universal-piece.png?w=1200\" alt=\"Spin Fruit Power from the Universal Piece Roblox experience.\"/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003eSpin\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e+\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e Best DPS of all Rare Fruit Powers\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e−\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e Relatively small AoE\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e−\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e Short range\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eB\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/kilo-fruit-power-universal-piece.png?w=1200\" alt=\"Kilo Fruit Power from the Universal Piece Roblox experience.\"/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003eKilo\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e+\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e Decent AoE and DPS\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e−\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e Long cooldowns and animations\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003eC\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/explodeman-fruit-power-universal-piece.png?w=1200\" alt=\"Explode Man Fruit Power from the Universal Piece Roblox experience.\"/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003eExplode Man\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e+\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e Decent DPS\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e−\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e Only useful for grinding in the first few islands\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003eC\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/hippo-fruit-power-universal-piece.png?w=1200\" alt=\"\"/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003eHippo\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e−\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e Only use it if you have literally no other Fruit Power\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003eC\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003c/tbody\u003e\u003c/table\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"h-how-to-get-new-fruit-powers-in-universal-piece\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003eHow to Get New Fruit Powers in Universal Piece\u003c/h2\u003e    \u003cfigure data-current-count=\"0\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003e \u003cfigure data-wp-context=\"{\u0026#34;imageId\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;681e949f78d92\u0026#34;}\" data-wp-interactive=\"core/image\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" data-wp-class--hide=\"state.isContentHidden\" data-wp-class--show=\"state.isContentVisible\" data-wp-init=\"callbacks.setButtonStyles\" data-wp-on-async--click=\"actions.showLightbox\" data-wp-on-async--load=\"callbacks.setButtonStyles\" data-wp-on-async-window--resize=\"callbacks.setButtonStyles\" data-id=\"1025846\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/universal-piece-fruit-power-gacha-npc.webp?resize=1200%2C675\" alt=\"Location of the Fruit Power Gacha NPC that lets you roll for a random Fruit Power using Gems in the Universal Piece Roblox experience.\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eYou can use Gems to get a random Fruit Power at the Power Gacha NPC, which is located on a few different islands.\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e    \u003cfigure data-wp-context=\"{\u0026#34;imageId\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;681e949f79265\u0026#34;}\" data-wp-interactive=\"core/image\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" data-wp-class--hide=\"state.isContentHidden\" data-wp-class--show=\"state.isContentVisible\" data-wp-init=\"callbacks.setButtonStyles\" data-wp-on-async--click=\"actions.showLightbox\" data-wp-on-async--load=\"callbacks.setButtonStyles\" data-wp-on-async-window--resize=\"callbacks.setButtonStyles\" data-id=\"1025848\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/universal-piece-fruit-power-dealer-npc.webp?resize=1200%2C675\" alt=\"Location of the Fruit Power Dealer NPC that lets you access the Power Shop in the Universal Piece Roblox experience.\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eThe Power Shop stock refreshes every hour, and only a select few Fruit Powers can be bought from it using Gems.\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003c/figure\u003e    \u003cp data-characters=\"107\" data-current-count=\"107\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003eThere are several ways to get one of the Fruit Powers from our tier list in Universal Piece, and those are:\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cul data-found-items=\"4\" data-current-count=\"267\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDefeating World Bosses\u003c/strong\u003e — \u003cstrong\u003eWorld Bosses spawn every once in a while\u003c/strong\u003e, and you always get a \u003cstrong\u003echat notification\u003c/strong\u003e when that happens.\u003c/li\u003e    \u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eRolling on the Power Gacha\u003c/strong\u003e — You can \u003cstrong\u003espend either\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e100\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e600\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e, or \u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003e15,000\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003eGems\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eto get one random Fruit Power\u003c/strong\u003e. By spending more \u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003eGems\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e, you have better odds of getting very rare Fruit Powers.\u003c/li\u003e    \u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePurchasing them in the Power Shop\u003c/strong\u003e — In the Power Shop, you can buy certain Fruit Powers that are in stock using \u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003eGems\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e. The \u003cstrong\u003ePower Shop stock refreshes every hour\u003c/strong\u003e. Also, most Fruit Powers in the game are available here in exchange for Robux.\u003c/li\u003e    \u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePurchasing bundles from the Robux Shop\u003c/strong\u003e — Several \u003cstrong\u003ebundles\u003c/strong\u003e in the Robux Shop \u003cstrong\u003econtain rare Fruit Powers\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/li\u003e \u003c/ul\u003e    \u003ch3 id=\"h-how-to-store-and-delete-fruit-powers\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003eHow to Store and Delete Fruit Powers\u003c/h3\u003e    \u003cfigure data-current-count=\"267\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003e \u003cfigure data-wp-context=\"{\u0026#34;imageId\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;681e949f7990f\u0026#34;}\" data-wp-interactive=\"core/image\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" data-wp-class--hide=\"state.isContentHidden\" data-wp-class--show=\"state.isContentVisible\" data-wp-init=\"callbacks.setButtonStyles\" data-wp-on-async--click=\"actions.showLightbox\" data-wp-on-async--load=\"callbacks.setButtonStyles\" data-wp-on-async-window--resize=\"callbacks.setButtonStyles\" data-id=\"1025844\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/universal-piece-fruit-power-inventory.webp?resize=1200%2C675\" alt=\"Preview of the inventory menu in the Universal Piece Roblox experience.\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eYou can store a certain amount of Fruit Powers in your inventory for future use.\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e    \u003cfigure data-wp-context=\"{\u0026#34;imageId\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;681e949f79e77\u0026#34;}\" data-wp-interactive=\"core/image\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" data-wp-class--hide=\"state.isContentHidden\" data-wp-class--show=\"state.isContentVisible\" data-wp-init=\"callbacks.setButtonStyles\" data-wp-on-async--click=\"actions.showLightbox\" data-wp-on-async--load=\"callbacks.setButtonStyles\" data-wp-on-async-window--resize=\"callbacks.setButtonStyles\" data-id=\"1025845\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/universal-piece-delete-fruit-power-npc.webp?resize=1200%2C675\" alt=\"Location of the Delete Power NPC in Universal Piece Roblox experience that lets one delete their current Fruit Power.\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eYou can remove your current Fruit Power by talking to the Delete Power NPC.\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003c/figure\u003e    \u003cp data-characters=\"448\" data-current-count=\"715\" data-injectable=\"true\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTo store a Fruit Power\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003epress \u003c/strong\u003ethe attack button (\u003cstrong\u003eM1\u003c/strong\u003e) while it is selected on your quickbar. Then, select the \u003cstrong\u003eStore \u003c/strong\u003eoption from the menu that appears. Keep in mind that \u003cstrong\u003eyou can store only a few Fruit Powers in your inventory at a time\u003c/strong\u003e. If you want \u003cstrong\u003eto throw away a Fruit Power\u003c/strong\u003e, hold it out and select the \u003cstrong\u003eDrop \u003c/strong\u003eor \u003cstrong\u003eReject \u003c/strong\u003eoptions. \u003cstrong\u003eTo destroy a Fruit Power\u003c/strong\u003e you equipped, visit the \u003cstrong\u003eDelete Power NPC\u003c/strong\u003e, which can be found on most islands in Universal Piece.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp data-characters=\"264\" data-current-count=\"264\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThat concludes our Universal Piece Fruit Power Tier List. Now, you have an idea of what Fruit Powers are worth the grind. If you want to claim some free \u003cmark\u003eGems\u003c/mark\u003e and start rolling for rare Fruit Powers right away, then make sure to check out our \u003ca href=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/universal-piece-codes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eUniversal Piece codes\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e    \u003chr data-injectable=\"false\"/\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"h-universal-piece-fruit-power-tier-list-faqs\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003eUniversal Piece Fruit Power Tier List FAQs\u003c/h2\u003e    \u003cdiv data-current-count=\"264\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"faq-question-1746718712903\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat are the best Fruit Powers in Universal Piece?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eCurrently, the best Fruit Powers in Universal Piece are \u003cmark\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSystem Breaker\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e, \u003cmark\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKing of Curse\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e, \u003cmark\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTurbo Exorcist\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003eLight\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv id=\"faq-question-1746730751209\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat Fruit Powers are the best in the early game?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eUseful early-game Fruit Powers are \u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003eLight\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003eBomb\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003e\u003cmark\u003eGas\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv id=\"faq-question-1746730814946\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCan you store a Fruit Power you have already equipped?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eUnfortunately, \u003cstrong\u003eyou can’t store a Fruit Power after you equip it\u003c/strong\u003e; you can only delete it.\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\u003chr/